{"tid":2025102,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"六四晚會有感而發","createTime":"2020-05-20T04:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T15:57:52.000Z","uid":278068,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b914de87b286c2816f3f5a5f1035c45e4dc669e","tid":2025102,"uid":278068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"六月四日的晚會就一定比人收皮<br />\n不如每人買枝電子蠟燭（餐廳係情人節擺係檯到呃錢會好feel啲果枝）去一路食黃店一路擺檯上面，之後post Twitter, Facebook, Instagram tag返六四之類<br />\n<br />\n我哋一定唔夠中共財多多、人多多、仆街多，但係我哋最叻最勁嘅係「創意」，一樣比香港政府不斷打壓、踐踏、無視的野<br />\n<br />\n抗爭生活化<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDA5SFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDA5SFP.png&h=63ad3212&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce349cd905846e06f96c5e0b17aaa60a8405cb7d","tid":2025102,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"idea 唔錯"},{"pid":"3ef03cdabe61736061b2e0ce89e5c724f77f8eae","tid":2025102,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"一向都覺得六四晚會好左膠<br />\n唉 今年都會係我第一次點下蠟燭做左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唏噓⋯⋯<br />\n但今年燭光一定會遍地開花"},{"pid":"71ba4a980a81a58574089795732836c0e0682719","tid":2025102,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"453a60653dc427a3e9b23191aef583a0719d1766","tid":2025102,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"我反而想黑警係64出水炮車占占占 人呀"}]}